| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2546 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 9df97882-88b7-54f5-9ce2-28c8a9ecbfe1"
